Curious if you really need to spend hundreds on the latest Apple tech? I put together a complete Apple ecosystem (iPhone, MacBook, Apple Watch, and iPad) for the same price as just the new iPhone 16e. The results were... interesting. Is this budget setup actually usable in 2025, or a complete waste of money?
